544
00:30:10,964 --> 00:30:14,127
- I only use his name when necessary. - How's your drink?

545
00:30:13,333 --> 00:30:14,857
-你的酒还好吗？ -很好

546
00:30:14,268 --> 00:30:17,669
- Fine. - Now I'll show you something beautiful.

547
00:30:15,001 --> 00:30:17,469
到这边来 让你看看真正漂亮的东西

548
00:30:17,804 --> 00:30:20,705
You do appreciate beauty, don't you?

549
00:30:17,837 --> 00:30:19,668
你的眼光应该不错吧？

550
00:30:23,343 --> 00:30:26,335
There you are. 600,000 dollars on four hoofs.

551
00:30:23,443 --> 00:30:26,071
这里！这匹马价值六十万元

552
00:30:26,246 --> 00:30:30,114
我敢说俄国沙皇 也从未在马身上花那么大笔钱

553
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:30,109
I bet Russian czars never paid that for a single horse.

554
00:30:30,250 --> 00:30:31,774
Khartoum.

555
00:30:30,617 --> 00:30:31,914
达通！

556
00:30:32,786 --> 00:30:34,048
Khartoum.

557
00:30:32,852 --> 00:30:34,217
达通！

