562
00:30:43,196 --> 00:30:45,130
我们去吃点东西吧！

563
00:30:43,664 --> 00:30:46,690
Let's get something to eat.

564
00:30:46,833 --> 00:30:50,098
Corleone is Johnny's godfather.

565
00:30:46,866 --> 00:30:49,528
柯里昂是强尼的教父

566
