634
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:58,039
In Sicily he has plants to process them into heroin.

635
00:34:54,280 --> 00:34:57,215
在西西里有工厂提练成海洛因

636
00:34:58,185 --> 00:35:01,621
He needs cash, he needs protection from the police.

637
00:34:58,251 --> 00:34:59,843
他需要现金

638
00:35:00,019 --> 00:35:03,682
以及在毒品交易时 需要警方的保护

639
00:35:01,755 --> 00:35:05,691
He'll give a piece of the action. I don't know how much.

640
00:35:03,856 --> 00:35:05,653
我无法查出保护费价钱多少

641
00:35:05,792 --> 00:35:08,590
在纽约是塔塔基利亚家族 在保护他

642
00:35:05,826 --> 00:35:11,025
The Tattaglia family is behind him here. They have to be in it for something.

643
00:35:08,761 --> 00:35:10,388
他们一定也想分占利益

644
00:35:10,797 --> 00:35:11,991
山尼柯里昂

645
00:35:12,032 --> 00:35:16,799
- What about his prison record? - One term in Italy, one here.

646
00:35:12,265 --> 00:35:15,962
-他的犯罪前科呢？ -一次在意大利，一次在这

647
00:35:16,937 --> 00:35:19,405
He's known as a top narcotics man.

648
00:35:17,003 --> 00:35:19,369
他是众所周知的大毒枭

649
00:35:19,539 --> 00:35:24,977
- Santino, what do you think? - A lot of money in that white powder.

650
00:35:19,872 --> 00:35:21,931
山提诺，你认为呢？

651
00:35:23,209 --> 00:35:24,733
白粉可以赚大钱

652
00:35:26,813 --> 00:35:28,110
Tom?

653
00:35:28,114 --> 00:35:32,278
